{"tid":2120924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官媒刊文指鄱陽湖「洪災也不是一個徹頭徹腦的壞東西 更帶來了重生和偉大的抗洪精神」","createTime":"2020-07-23T03:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T13:57:17.000Z","uid":13663,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4ab4b234d1a930f4e81c08fae2746747fc0c34","tid":2120924,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"長江流域連日暴雨，已經出現多次洪水，江西鄱陽縣鄱陽湖周邊的處圩堤出現潰決，不少民眾的房屋被洪水淹浸，是災情最慘重的地方之一。可是當地縣委主辦的官媒昨日（21日）發文，題為「洪災也不是一個徹頭徹腦的壞東西」，形容「洪災不至於壞到透頂」，引發外界質疑，批評這種說法根本是何不食肉糜，事件被廣傳後，當局已把文章刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200722/W3JWTB2AJSRBVUPP7OBMXJWTW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FW3JWTB2AJSRBVUPP7OBMXJWTW4%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=d9008507\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FW3JWTB2AJSRBVUPP7OBMXJWTW4%2F&h=3f1bd642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200722/W3JWTB2AJSRBVUPP7OBMXJWTW4/</a>"},{"pid":"38ebfe1938874ef0371fa23b4ba6ed1f006c91d5","tid":2120924,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"正能樣！👍🏻👍🏻"},{"pid":"4ac3e3da6c05fc36f7ec93db99f462e929cc03a5","tid":2120924,"uid":12628,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"土也肥了，水也足了，gdp又長了，雖然我命沒了"},{"pid":"e9f7fffcd5775109f77a678eceb76d994d16f178","tid":2120924,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7Tkj35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7Tkj35.jpg&h=c0ec8b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算有10級地震都唔撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ce5bca4879caf024ba69afc11371aaf7125cc3","tid":2120924,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-2